# Partenaire v2.0 — STAGING build env for the MP web/admin frontend.
# Loaded only when building with `--mode staging` (see the staging Vercel
# project's Build Command), so it never affects the prod build (.env.production).
# Points the React app at the STAGING MP backend so v2 testing never hits prod.
